   External Data Center

Geographic Information System (GIS)
   __________________________________________________________________

   The ARC/INFO Geographical Information System is used to maintain
   information on surface characterization data for Barrow, AK, the area
   in which the ARM NSA CART site is located.
   __________________________________________________________________

